WEBVTT

00:04.913 --> 00:05.631
ï»¿We've been robbed!

00:05.829 --> 00:06.056
What?

00:07.681 --> 00:08.921
They took everything!

00:09.074 --> 00:09.683
They took Buddy.

00:11.224 --> 00:12.073
Well, where are you going?

00:12.201 --> 00:13.131
I'm gonna go and get my dog!

00:14.133 --> 00:15.000
I didn't see anything.

00:15.245 --> 00:16.662
They stole my dog.

00:16.863 --> 00:18.547
A delicacy in my country, right?

00:18.928 --> 00:19.989
