00:20.218 --> 00:20.737
You thought it.

00:22.405 --> 00:23.580
I'm gonna need your help, John.

00:25.326 --> 00:25.931
Okay.

00:26.646 --> 00:27.943
Wear extra underpants.

00:29.409 --> 00:29.933
