00:32.869 --> 00:33.965
So, you want the dog back?

00:35.747 --> 00:36.534
It's the only thing I want.

00:36.655 --> 00:39.881
Lupe took your dog and a briefcase full of my cocaine.

00:40.111 --> 00:41.799
You find her, I'll give your dog back.

00:42.040 --> 00:43.092
Got an address on that?

00:43.311 --> 00:44.135
Google it, homes.

00:48.502 --> 00:49.001
What are you doing?

00:50.705 --> 00:52.170
I gotta go steal back some drugs...

00:54.406 --> 00:55.680
...then get my dog back.

00:56.079 --> 00:56.620
Wanna come?

00:56.905 --> 00:57.826
It sounds like fun.

00:58.167 --> 00:58.965
Could be dangerous.

01:00.168 --> 01:00.793
Maybe I'll die.

